---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Who We Serve | Retirement Planning for Utah Families | Capital Wealth Advisors"
description: "Capital Wealth Advisors serves retirees, diligent savers with $500K+, and tax-conscious planners in Utah and nationwide. Learn if we're the right fit for you."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
  - { name: "Who We Serve", url: "/who-we-serve/" }
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Who We Serve</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">We work with families who have saved diligently and want expert guidance to make the most of their retirement.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Client Profiles -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-xl">
            <h2>Our Ideal Clients</h2>
            <p class="text-lg">We specialize in working with families who share these characteristics.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-3">
            {% for client in site.whoWeServe %}
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="text-accent">{{ client.title }}</h3>
                <p>{{ client.description }}</p>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Detailed Profiles -->
<section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-xl">Do Any of These Sound Like You?</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Approaching Retirement (Age 55-65)</h3>
                <p>You've spent decades saving and are now within striking distance of retirement. You need answers to critical questions:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <li>Do I have enough to retire?</li>
                    <li>When should I claim Social Security?</li>
                    <li>How do I turn savings into income?</li>
                    <li>What about healthcare before Medicare?</li>
                    <li>How will taxes change in retirement?</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/services/retirement-money-map/" class="btn btn-secondary mt-lg">See Our Planning Process</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Recently Retired (Age 62-70)</h3>
                <p>You've made the leap into retirement and need to optimize your new financial reality:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <li>Am I withdrawing from the right accounts?</li>
                    <li>Should I do Roth conversions now?</li>
                    <li>How do I navigate Medicare and IRMAA?</li>
                    <li>Is my portfolio positioned correctly?</li>
                    <li>What about Required Minimum Distributions?</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/services/tax-planning/" class="btn btn-secondary mt-lg">Tax-Efficient Strategies</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Established Retirees (Age 70+)</h3>
                <p>You've been retired for years and want to preserve and transfer your wealth:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <li>How do I manage RMDs efficiently?</li>
                    <li>Is my estate plan up to date?</li>
                    <li>Am I being tax-efficient with withdrawals?</li>
                    <li>Should I consider charitable strategies?</li>
                    <li>Is my portfolio still appropriate?</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/services/estate-planning/" class="btn btn-secondary mt-lg">Legacy Planning</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Federal Employees</h3>
                <p>You have a unique benefits package that requires specialized knowledge:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <li>How do I maximize my FERS annuity?</li>
                    <li>What's the best TSP strategy for me?</li>
                    <li>Should I keep FEGLI into retirement?</li>
                    <li>How does FEHB work with Medicare?</li>
                    <li>When is the optimal time to retire?</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/services/federal-benefits/" class="btn btn-secondary mt-lg">Federal Benefits Planning</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Minimum Requirements -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Minimum Requirements</h2>
            <p class="text-lg">To provide the level of service our clients expect, we work with families who have:</p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 mt-xl">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="case-study-metric">$500K+</div>
                    <div class="case-study-label">Retirement Savings</div>
                    <p class="mt-md">Enough savings to benefit from comprehensive planning strategies.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="case-study-metric">Retirement</div>
                    <div class="case-study-label">Focus Area</div>
                    <p class="mt-md">Approaching retirement, recently retired, or already in retirement.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="case-study-metric">Partnership</div>
                    <div class="case-study-label">Mindset</div>
                    <p class="mt-md">Willing to engage in a collaborative, ongoing planning relationship.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Think We Might Be the Right Fit?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg">Schedule a complimentary consultation to discuss your situation and how we can help.</p>

            <div class="hero-cta mt-lg">
                <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Schedule a Consultation</a>
                <a href="tel:{{ site.phone }}" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Call {{ site.phone }}</a>
            </div>

            <p class="mt-md text-muted">No obligation. No pressure. Just a conversation about your financial future.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>